      <div class="reason-card"><div class="service-card-header"><div class="reason-icon">🩻</div><h4>Pseudomyxoma Peritonei</h4></div><p>Appendix-origin mucinous tumour. CRS+HIPEC is potentially curative using the Sugarbaker technique.</p></div>
