      <div class="reason-card"><div class="service-card-header"><div class="reason-icon">🩻</div><h4>Ovarian Cancer Debulking</h4></div><p>Interval debulking with HIPEC. OVHIPEC trial (NEJM 2018).</p></div>
      <div class="reason-card"><div class="service-card-header"><div class="reason-icon">🩻</div><h4>Gastric Peritoneal Metastases</h4></div><p>Carefully selected cases. Tumor Board evaluation mandatory.</p></div>
